settings.description: You and your crew are on vacation when a anomaly strikes your ship and you and your crew evacuates! You find your ship safe but 4 of your crewmates are missing! Find them! Based off: VVVVVV
#8993-090 = Jump from block to block in order to escape the unexpectedly deadly opera center.
Mario finds himself in a World with water, can he escape to cloud land? Base of operations of M and L are ahead, so be quick!
A nuclear reactor powering Smaghetti’s servers. It’s being shut down for bogus reasons such as, “hazardous wastes”, and, “dangerous for the earth”. No Co2, just waste that can be buried really deep.
Thwomps and Thwimps! this place is full to the brim with these mad rocky foes! think you can make it out of these ruins without getting crushed?
